<subSubSection pageId="30" pageNumber="30" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="30.[140,450,1109,1133]" box="[140,450,1109,1133]" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">
Tribe: 
<taxonomicName authority="Dumort." authorityName="Dumort." box="[210,450,1109,1133]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="30" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="tribe" tribe="Cardamineae">
<emphasis box="[210,346,1109,1133]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">Cardamineae</emphasis>
Dumort.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[112,765,1173,1421]" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis box="[140,203,1174,1197]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">Notes.</emphasis>
– A genus of five species, of which two are native to North America, one in 
<collectingCountry box="[369,466,1206,1229]" name="Morocco" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">Morocco</collectingCountry>
, one European species, and another a crop and cosmopolitan weed naturalized throughout world (
<bibRefCitation author="AL-SHEHBAZ, I. A. &amp; R. A. PRICE" box="[190,505,1269,1293]" pageId="30" pageNumber="30" pagination="124 - 126" refId="ref135315" refString="AL-SHEHBAZ, I. A. &amp; R. A. PRICE (1998). Delimitation of the genus Nasturtium (Brassicaceae). Novon 8: 124 - 126." type="journal article" year="1998">AL-SHEHBAZ &amp; PRICE, 1998</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[112,765,1173,1421]" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">
The genus was so broadly delimited by 
<bibRefCitation author="KUNTZE, C. E. O." box="[570,733,1301,1325]" pageId="30" pageNumber="30" refId="ref140653" refString="KUNTZE, C. E. O. (1891). Revisio genera plantarum 2. Leipzig." type="book" year="1891">KUNTZE (1891)</bibRefCitation>
to include more than 50 species, but most other earlier authors, including Boissier in 
<emphasis box="[360,541,1365,1389]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">Flora Orientalis,</emphasis>
circumscribed it to include species currently assigned to 
<taxonomicName box="[511,604,1397,1421]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Barbarea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="30" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[511,604,1397,1421]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">Barbarea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J.A.Scopoli" authorityYear="1760" box="[656,739,1398,1421]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Rorippa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="30" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[656,739,1398,1421]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="30">Rorippa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
